data.description: Welcome to this exquisite colonial nestled on a pristine, flat 1/2 acre property in Fort Salonga. This home boasts 4/5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing plenty of space and unparalleled living experience. The home greets you with an abundance of natural light, giving the house a warm and inviting feel. The living and dining areas create a perfect space for entertaining, while the family room, complete with a cozy wood burning fireplace, offers a more intimate space for relaxation and entertaining. The kitchen offers ample amounts of counterspace along with a sun room/large eat-in area with access to the backyard. There are two options for primary bedrooms (one on the first floor and one on the second floor). Step outside and you'll be surrounded by perfectly manicured grounds and breathtaking scenery. The large deck is perfect for entertaining guests and hosting events. The home is located in the highly desirable Beverly Beach neighborhood and has access to its own private beach with a nominal fee. Close Proximity To Northport Village, Highways, Shopping, and Restaurants. Gorgeous Winter Waterviews.
